'''Unit Theta''' was a military unit of the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]].

The unit was a part of the unit of infiltrators known as [[Scandium Team]]. It was notorious for its high degree of success, and infamous because of its equally high casualty rates.

